text: Irish Women's Cup may refer to: * IFA Women's Challenge Cup, the senior cup competition of women's football teams in Northern Ireland. * FAI Women's Cup, the senior cup competition for women's association football teams in the Republic of Ireland. * Irish Senior Cup (women's hockey), a knockout trophy played for by field hockey clubs in Ireland. * Irish Junior Cup (women's hockey), a knockout trophy played for by field hockey clubs in Ireland.
title: Irish Women's Cup
